[center][b]OBJECTIVE[/b][/center]
[center]
The goal is to have the majority of the discs on the board showing your color at the end of the game.
[/center]
[center][b]THE RULES[/b][/center]

[center]1. Black always moves first.
2. You must place a disc such that it sandwiches one or more opponent discs between your new disc and another disc of your color.
